title: What are good songs on Lil Wayne's new album 'I'm not a human being'? - Quora

response.answer_text: Though previously released as a single, "Right Above It" received positive reviews and ranked highly on the music charts. In the song, Lil Wayne quotes Tupak Shakur's famous lyrics, "I ain't a killer but don't push me."
